00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.140
Do you feel better?

00:01:39.260 --> 00:01:41.260
Hmm...

00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:00.820
Mork...

00:02:05.020 --> 00:02:06.380
Who?

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:14.900
Pardon?

