Don't you really remember?

00:02:44.860 --> 00:02:46.740
If you're good to me...

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:49.300
because you think that I'm Mork,

00:02:51.740 --> 00:02:53.220
I have to say thank you.

00:03:05.600 --> 00:03:06.420
Mork!

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:07.520
Mork...

00:03:14.900 --> 00:03:15.980
I always understand that...

00:03:19.060 --> 00:03:21.060
you can remember me.

00:03:26.780 --> 00:03:29.540
This is the second time that you walk away from me!

00:03:33.900 --> 00:03:38.020
Didn't I love you enough?

00:03:41.060 --> 00:03:43.060
Why me?

00:03:43.540 --> 00:03:45.060
I'm always the one who is disappointed in love.

00:04:32.460 --> 00:04:34.460
I'm sorry.

00:04:42.100 --> 00:04:44.100
I'm sorry that I didn't tell you...

00:04:52.020 --> 00:04:54.020
At first, I was so angry.

00:05:01.580 --> 00:05:03.580
But now I understand.

00:05:06.740 --> 00:05:08.740
It's difficult for you to tell me.

00:05:11.860 --> 00:05:13.860
Because you're afraid that I would be sad.

00:05:28.260 --> 00:05:30.260
Mork...

00:05:41.100 --> 00:05:43.100
I like you.

00:06:03.700 --> 00:06:05.700
I think...

00:06:06.220 --> 00:06:07.700
I'm too young...

00:06:09.700 --> 00:06:11.700
to love someone.

00:06:24.340 --> 00:06:26.780
The relationship that can't go on

00:06:31.740 --> 00:06:33.740
or can't stop loving...

00:06:37.420 --> 00:06:39.420
is too cruel.

00:06:45.820 --> 00:06:49.140
Please don't think that just only you who are heartbroken.

00:06:51.980 --> 00:06:53.980
You know what...

00:06:57.740 --> 00:06:59.740
The worst thing is that

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:03.740
you're always by my side...

00:07:09.420 --> 00:07:11.900
but I still feel so lonely...

00:07:13.900 --> 00:07:16.180
I want to accept your love...

00:07:16.180 --> 00:07:18.180
without embarrassing anyone.

00:07:19.860 --> 00:07:21.860
Do you understand?

00:07:24.820 --> 00:07:27.420
I don't know what kind of feeling I'm feeling right now.

00:07:30.780 --> 00:07:32.780
I can't be falling in love with anyone...

00:07:36.460 --> 00:07:39.740
I still don't understand what I'm feeling for you...

00:07:42.620 --> 00:07:44.620
I think I don't understand myself.

00:07:48.180 --> 00:07:50.180
If you say that you can't be falling in love with anyone...

00:07:56.540 --> 00:07:58.540
Can I beg you one thing?

00:08:01.300 --> 00:08:04.180
Let me love you as you are...

00:08:04.940 --> 00:08:06.660
Please...

00:08:21.380 --> 00:08:23.380
You think that our relationship right now...

00:08:27.740 --> 00:08:29.740
is not so clear?

00:08:36.500 --> 00:08:38.500
I think we shouldn't fight.

00:08:40.820 --> 00:08:43.980
It's awful to be far away from you.

00:08:48.020 --> 00:08:50.020
I promise...

00:08:54.700 --> 00:08:56.700
I'm going to come back here to give you my answer.

00:09:24.620 --> 00:09:26.620
Please listen carefully...

00:09:29.740 --> 00:09:32.620
I'll be right here waiting for you and your answer...

00:09:42.140 --> 00:09:44.140
until you come back.

00:10:34.100 --> 00:10:35.460
You're loser again.

