00:12:33.140 --> 00:12:38.940
During 99 days, you have to come and get the first dew of winter from me before midnight.

00:13:15.180 --> 00:13:16.740
Let's go inside.

00:13:23.740 --> 00:13:25.740
P'Mek...

00:13:26.340 --> 00:13:27.740
Hello...

00:13:29.380 --> 00:13:31.380
P'Mek...

00:13:33.620 --> 00:13:35.380
P'Mek...

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:39.500
Where is P'Mek?

00:13:39.500 --> 00:13:42.740
I want to meet and talk to him.

00:13:44.740 --> 00:13:46.740
Let's go somewhere else.

00:13:46.740 --> 00:13:47.860
Just a moment.

00:13:47.860 --> 00:13:49.860
Where are you going?

00:13:49.860 --> 00:13:51.860
I'm going back home.

00:13:51.860 --> 00:13:53.860
I don't think so.

00:13:54.900 --> 00:13:59.020
If you go back home right now, you still can't enter your house.

00:13:59.020 --> 00:14:01.020
Why? It's not so far.

00:14:01.700 --> 00:14:03.020
Please believe what I say.

00:14:03.020 --> 00:14:07.060
Let's hang out, please...

00:14:07.060 --> 00:14:08.660
Up to you.

00:14:08.660 --> 00:14:10.700
Thanks. Let's go!

00:14:35.100 --> 00:14:37.100
I think white clothes are perfect for you.

00:14:42.940 --> 00:14:47.540
Mork, Mork...

00:15:02.380 --> 00:15:03.380
Excuse me

00:15:03.380 --> 00:15:03.860
Yes?

00:15:03.860 --> 00:15:05.860
Where are you going?

00:15:07.860 --> 00:15:09.860
I'm looking for my brother.

00:15:09.860 --> 00:15:13.660
It seems like the cafe is closing now. I think he's going back home.

00:15:13.660 --> 00:15:15.660
Can I help you?

00:15:15.660 --> 00:15:18.020
It's not the right time to go back home.

00:15:20.020 --> 00:15:22.020
Why not?

00:15:25.060 --> 00:15:29.780
In this world, everything happens for a reason.

00:15:37.780 --> 00:15:39.780
Who are you?

00:15:40.900 --> 00:15:44.580
I'm trusting and wondering...

00:15:46.580 --> 00:15:51.100
I'm monitoring and controlling...

00:15:51.100 --> 00:15:53.100
Huh?

00:15:53.100 --> 00:15:57.100
Are you acting like an angel?

00:15:57.100 --> 00:16:00.620
I don't believe you.

00:16:02.620 --> 00:16:05.620
Apparently, you're surrounded by weird things, aren't you?

00:16:18.900 --> 00:16:20.220
Mon is still here.

00:16:20.220 --> 00:16:22.220
Wait...

00:16:23.900 --> 00:16:25.900
You can't go inside

00:16:25.900 --> 00:16:30.020
until you have to promise me.

00:16:32.820 --> 00:16:38.380
If you go inside, you have to come back before midnight.

00:16:38.380 --> 00:16:41.220
What crazy are you saying?

00:16:41.220 --> 00:16:43.220
Stop asking, just listening!

00:16:46.100 --> 00:16:47.940
You don't have so much time.

00:16:52.140 --> 00:16:56.860
You're going to meet that person for the last time.

00:17:01.060 --> 00:17:03.060
He doesn't have a chance to see you again.

00:17:07.260 --> 00:17:09.700
He's in another world. His world is different from ours.

00:17:14.900 --> 00:17:16.900
What?

00:17:16.900 --> 00:17:18.900
Mon...

00:17:25.900 --> 00:17:31.460
I'm going to let that person meet you for the last time.

00:17:40.500 --> 00:17:42.500
It's your time now.

00:17:46.780 --> 00:17:48.780
Don't forget what I told you.

00:17:53.380 --> 00:17:55.380
Come back here before midnight.

00:18:41.060 --> 00:18:41.780
Mon...

00:18:56.940 --> 00:18:59.100
I'm Mork. You're Mon.

00:19:02.500 --> 00:19:04.500
I'm Mork.

00:19:09.900 --> 00:19:11.900
You're loser.

00:19:15.900 --> 00:19:19.700
Hmm. Yes, I am.

00:19:33.300 --> 00:19:36.220
You like the stranger game, don't you?

00:19:39.460 --> 00:19:41.460
How many years

00:19:44.820 --> 00:19:46.820
that I'm Mork playing as Mon,

00:19:49.860 --> 00:19:51.860
and you're Mon playing as Mork?

00:19:58.740 --> 00:20:00.740
I don't know.

00:20:00.740 --> 00:20:02.740
Why?

00:20:02.740 --> 00:20:04.740
Do you want to play again?

00:20:21.820 --> 00:20:23.820
No, I don't.

00:20:30.980 --> 00:20:32.980
What's up, P'Mon?

00:20:34.020 --> 00:20:36.180
How are you?

00:20:40.980 --> 00:20:42.980
I'm sorry...

00:20:44.980 --> 00:20:46.980
that I ask you to play this crazy game.

00:20:50.300 --> 00:20:56.060
If we did not play this game, you would not be apart.

00:21:01.220 --> 00:21:02.980
It's also my fault.

00:21:04.980 --> 00:21:06.980
Don't blame yourself.

00:21:20.780 --> 00:21:24.020
It's been 3 years since you left home.

00:21:27.660 --> 00:21:29.660
I've not been in relationship with P'Tiew.

00:21:32.340 --> 00:21:34.340
I know P'Tiew likes you so much.

00:21:43.420 --> 00:21:47.180
I just want to end this by two of you.

00:21:57.940 --> 00:21:59.940
So we understand, right?

00:22:03.500 --> 00:22:11.180
From now on, you don't have to worry about me.

00:22:16.260 --> 00:22:18.380
I forgive you for everything.

00:22:43.260 --> 00:22:51.500
What makes me most happy is that the two of us were born together.

